Package: ptef
Type: Package
Title: PTEF - Pronunciation-Time Estimation Framework for Brazilian Portuguese
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("PTEF", "Team", email = "ptef@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A probabilistic framework for estimating pronunciation time of numerical sequences in Brazilian Portuguese. Implements O(log N) algorithms for token counting, lognormal duration models, and prosodic pause estimation.
